items.name: Searching in the Flex Platform
items.description: (406) In this module, we cover how to search in the Flex platform. We go through the various search options and how to best search inside of Ooyala Flex.

items.name: Intro to Ooyala Discovery
items.description: In this tutorial we discuss Ooyala's most recent product OOYALA Discovery

items.name: Intro to Ooyala Discovery
items.description: In this tutorial we discuss Ooyala's most recent product Ooyala Discovery.

items.name: Monitoring Resources in Flex
items.description: (410) In this module, we cover how to monitor the various types of resources that are running inside of Flex.

items.name: Using Kibana Dashboard for Analytics
items.description: (411) Analytics is very important for Flex customers. In this module, we cover how to use the Kibana Dashboard to view and save all of the analytical data from Flex.

items.name: Monitoring Jobs in Flex
items.description: (409) In this module, we cover how to monitor jobs in of Ooyala Flex. We cover the workflow dashboard and how this can be used to monitor real-time running jobs too. Monitoring allows actions to be carried out if required in Flex in real-time.

items.name: Workflows in Flex
items.description: (408) Workflows are very important in Flex! In this module, we cover how to run and view workflows in Ooyala Flex as well as how to debug workflow problems. A workflow is an ordered sequence of tasks that are carried out to fulfill a business or technical process.

items.name: Managing Assets in Flex
items.description: (405) In this module, we go over how to manage assets in Flex. We cover this using the Flex Core Platform and the Flex MAM application.

items.name: Triggering Jobs in Flex
items.description: (407) In this module, we cover what is a job and how to trigger jobs inside of Ooyala Flex. jobs are managed by Ooyala Flexs internal job scheduler. The job scheduler is responsible for that handling the storage, retrieval, prioritization, and execution of jobs.

items.name: Introduction to Flex and using the Flex UI
items.description:
In this module we give an introduction to Ooyala Flex, the Flex UI and what Ooyala Flex can be used for.
401

items.name: Flex Reviewer Overview
items.description:
In this module, we go over the main features and uses of the Flex Reviewer module. Reviewer lets you provide feedback and approve or decline assets.
404

items.name: Flex MAM Overview
items.description:
In this module, we go over the main features and uses of the Flex MAM module. MAM is a user-friendly way of viewing, managing and editing assets.
403

items.name: Flex Platform Feature Overview
items.description:
In the Flex Platform Feature Introduction module, we go over the Ooyala Flex architecture and the microservices that can be used with Flex.
